### Botones
```
Primary:
  bg #2B8FD4, texto blanco, rounded-lg, h-12
  pressed: opacity-80

Secondary:
  bg #f0f4f8, texto #0f172a, rounded-lg, h-12
  pressed: opacity-80

Danger:
  bg #ef4444, texto blanco, rounded-lg, h-12
