## BADGES DE ESTADO — MAPEO COMPLETO

**OrderStatus → badge:**
```
PENDING          → warning  → "Pendiente de pago"
PAID             → info     → "Pago confirmado"
PREPARING        → info     → "Preparando tu pedido"
READY_FOR_PICKUP → info     → "Listo para retirar"
COMPLETED        → success  → "Entregado"
CANCELED         → danger   → "Cancelado"
STOCK_ISSUE      → warning  → "Problema de stock"
```

**ProductStatus → badge (para referencia):**
```
ACTIVE             → success → "Activo"
PAUSED_BY_SELLER   → warning → "Pausado"
DISABLED_BY_ADMIN  → danger  → "No disponible"
```

**isVisible (reseñas):**
Solo mostrar reseñas donde `isVisible === true`. Las demás no se renderizan.

### Estilos de badge por variante
```tsx
// success
<View className="bg-success-bg px-2 py-1 rounded-full">
  <Text className="text-success-text text-xs font-medium">Entregado</Text>
</View>

// warning
<View className="bg-warning-bg px-2 py-1 rounded-full">
  <Text className="text-warning-text text-xs font-medium">Pendiente</Text>
</View>

// danger
<View className="bg-danger-bg px-2 py-1 rounded-full">
  <Text className="text-danger-text text-xs font-medium">Cancelado</Text>
</View>

// info
<View className="bg-info-bg px-2 py-1 rounded-full">
  <Text className="text-info-text text-xs font-medium">Preparando</Text>
</View>

// neutral
<View className="bg-neutral-bg px-2 py-1 rounded-full">
  <Text className="text-neutral-text text-xs font-medium">—</Text>
</View>
```

